      "width": 560,
      "height": 300,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Migration Notes\n\nDocument explicit, reversible evolution for:\n\n- authority ladder changes\n- semantic type renames\n- multiplicity changes\n- default root policy changes\n- boundary filtering behavior\n\nMigration notes must preserve portability and avoid silent authority escalation.",
